  "title": "Regional Sales Lead – Pipeline & Infrastructure (Oil & Gas) [EL]",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Lead regional sales planning and execution to drive sustainable growth.</p></li><li><p>Identify, secure, and grow key accounts in the steel line pipe market.</p></li><li><p>Manage high-value contract negotiations and commercial discussions.</p></li><li><p>Collaborate with cross-functional teams to deliver client-specific solutions.</p></li><li><p>Analyze market dynamics and competitor positioning to guide sales strategy.</p></li><li><p>Maintain accurate sales forecasts and reporting.</p></li><li><p>Ensure adherence to safety, quality, and regulatory requirements.</p></li><li><p>Travel frequently within Southeast Asia to support business development.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p>Degree in Engineering, Business Administration, or equivalent.</p></li><li><p>Minimum 8 years of sales experience in steel line pipe or related oil & gas products.</p></li><li><p>Proven ability to manage large accounts and deliver consistent results.</p></li><li><p>Strong knowledge of pipeline standards and project specifications.</p></li></ul><p><br />We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p><p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>",
